WEBVTT

00:01.770 --> 00:06.776
Japanese artist Yayoi Kusama is best known for her inexhaustible creations...

00:07.041 --> 00:10.701
...involving polka dots, pumpkins and vibrant colors.

00:11.515 --> 00:15.436
Her love of design has seen her join forces with top fashion houses...

00:15.747 --> 00:17.234
...creating her own ranges.

00:19.619 --> 00:22.596
She's also designed videos for the best in the pop world.

00:24.170 --> 00:29.084
Now on her ninth decade, Kusama continues to create every single day,...

00:29.534 --> 00:34.475
...her art as productive as when she first broke on the world stage in the 1960s.

